      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVOID THE NOISE (5) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.3 lengths back in second (22.06) at Q Lakeside in a Maiden over 390m. Well placed and gets his chance. QUICK FIFTY (4) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a nose (20.20) behind Hara's Collar at Q Lakeside. Racing well and deserves a win. MOTION ACTIVATED (8) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in six starts. Missed the frame when fifth (20.56) at this track latest but was in the placings the start before. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. One of the main contenders. JADE CLOVER (1) is by Sennachie out of Regal Jade making debut. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
